title: [Upper Dragonsclaw, Village]
description: A decrepit village lies sprawled in all directions.  Ragged tents lie in various states of disarray and small fires burn along the path.  Off to your side, a rabid mutt tears at the carcass of some small animal and snarls menacingly at you as it chews.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, east, southeast, southwest, northwest
